data.description: This 4bd 2ba home is located in Curtis Community just outside of Jasper. Take advantage of the country feel located between Jasper, TX and Lake Sam Rayburn. This farm house styled home features an open concept layout with a reading nook in the living room. The primary bedroom is split from the other 3 bedrooms for extra privacy. The laundry room is conveniently located close to the primary bedroom. Outside you will see the fully fenced in yard and storage building along with a carport. Make your appointment today to view this beautiful home.
